    "To cross this gap, we must understand the process underlying common explanations.",
    "In the first section of the paper, we explain the problems with the explanations offered within xAI.",
    "We argue that current xAI methods do little to help.",
    "The explanations on the offer do not reduce the ambiguity of AI decisions.",
    "Based on this, we must turn to social sciences and base our definition of explainability on everyday explanations."
